Note: List Secrets in a namespace
Process called "list_secrets" that takes namespace as Optional[String] returns List[KubernetesSecret]:
    Let command be "get secrets -o json"
    If namespace is not null:
        Set command to "get secrets -n " with message namespace with message " -o json"
